                </svg>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Join BookHub Today</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">Start building your personal library and connect with millions of book lovers worldwide.</p>
            </div>
            <div data-slot="card" class="bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm p-8 sm:p-10">
